          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681226038917-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is softening, combine your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in the reserved bowl with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>hoisin sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681226045952-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681226045952-x400.jpg",
